frontMatter.title: Free Python course material
frontMatter.summary: Free Python course materials! I put in a FOIA request to the NSA for their Python training materials and got back a 400-page printout of their COMP 3321 training course. So, I scanned and OCR'd it. Here is a PDF (warning: 118 MB) https://t.co/i1Fxe6G4MJ
